{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"HTMLContentElement.select","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLContentElement/select","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLContentElement\"><code>HTMLContentElement</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Propriedades</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLContentElement/getDistributedNodes\"><code>getDistributedNodes()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><em><code>select</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Páginas relacionadas a Web Components</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/CustomElementRegistry\"><code>CustomElementRegistry</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Document/createElement\"><code>Document.createElement()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/attachShadow\"><code>Element.attachShadow()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/shadowRoot\"><code>Element.shadowRoot</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/slot\"><code>Element.slot</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Event/composed\"><code>Event.composed</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Event/composedPath\"><code>Event.composedPath</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLSlotElement\"><code>HTMLSlotElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTemplateElement\"><code>HTMLTemplateElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/getRootNode\"><code>Node.getRootNode()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Node/isConnected\"><code>Node.isConnected</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ShadowRoot\"><code>ShadowRoot</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/customElements\"><code>Window.customElements</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>A propriedade&nbsp;<code><strong>HTMLContentElement.select</strong></code>&nbsp;reflete&nbsp;o atributo selecionado. É um&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>DOMString</code></a> contendo&nbsp;uma lista de&nbsp;spaço-separado&nbsp;de seletores&nbsp;CSS que seleciona&nbsp;o&nbsp;conteúdo&nbsp;para&nbsp;inserir&nbsp;em&nbsp;lugar&nbsp;do&nbsp;elemento &lt;content&gt;.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sintaxe","title":"Sintaxe","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><em>object</em>.select = \"<em>CSSselector</em> <em>CSSselector</em> ...\";\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"Exemplo","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">// Select &lt;h1&gt; elements and elements with class=\"error\"</span>\nmyContentObject<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>select <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"h1 .error\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications_2","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"spec-table standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificações</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Commentário</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/webcomponents/spec/shadow/#the-content-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Shadow DOM<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'content' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-obsolete\">Obsoleto</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect2\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Componente</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari (WebKit)</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte básico</td>\n   <td>35</td>\n   <td><span style=\"font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/28\" title=\"Released on 2014-03-18.\">28</a> (28)</span>&nbsp;[1]</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td>26</td>\n   <td><span style=\"font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;\"><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Phone</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte básico</td>\n   <td>37</td>\n   <td>28.0 (28) [1]</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<p>[1] Se Shadow DOM não estiver&nbsp;habilitado&nbsp;no&nbsp;Firefox, os elementos &lt;content&gt; se comportarão&nbsp;como <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLUnknownElement\"><code>HTMLUnknownElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>. Shadow DOM foi o primeiro&nbsp;implementado no&nbsp;Firefox 28 e está atrás&nbsp;de uma preferência, <code>dom.webcomponents.enabled</code>, ao qual é desabilitado por padrão.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"veja_também","title":"Veja também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLContentElement\">HTMLContentElement</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Sintaxe","id":"sintaxe"},{"text":"Exemplo","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Especificações","id":"specifications_2"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Veja também","id":"veja_também"}],"summary":"A propriedade HTMLContentElement.select reflete o atributo selecionado. É um DOMString contendo uma lista de spaço-separado de seletores CSS que seleciona o conteúdo para inserir em lugar do elemento <content>.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"HTMLContentElement.select","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"HTMLContentElement.select","locale":"fr","native":"Français"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/api/htmlcontentelement/select","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/api/htmlcontentelement/select/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API","title":"APIs da Web"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLContentElement","title":"HTMLContentElement"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLContentElement/select","title":"HTMLContentElement.select"}],"pageTitle":"HTMLContentElement.select - APIs da Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}